http://www.thehindu.com/news/cities/Vijayawada/Three-year-old-boy-drowns-in-water-tank/article14600116.ece

 A three-year-old boy, Venkatesh, who was playing in front of his house, drowned in a water tank in the Mahanandeeswara Nagar Colony at Mahanandi town in Kurnool district on Tuesday.The boy’s mother Sridevi spotted his body in the tank adjoining their house. On the advice of a local doctor, she rushed him to Nandyal, but the Government hospital doctors declared him as brought dead, according to police.